import React from 'react'
import { Provider } from 'react-redux'
import { BasicStore } from './ReduxStore'
import ReduxComp from './ReduxComp'

function Main() {


  return (
    <>  
            <Provider store={BasicStore}>
                <ReduxComp/>
            </Provider>

    
    </>
  )
}

export default Main
